QuestData.Title: The Prince is Going Down
QuestData.Description:
$n! I knew you'd come.
Quick, let me out of here and we'll take this giant down.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: Cast the giants into disarray by killing their prince.
QuestData.LogDescription: Free Okuna Longtusk and kill Prince Oceanus.
QuestData.RewardText:
With Oceanus dead, the skrogs will start fighting amongst themselves. They'll certainly be too busy to provide any further assistance to the naga.
I'd say this was a job well done, despite my being captured. Good thing you came along.
I'll see you around, $n.
